RLE

Class ParsedPattern

  • java.lang.Object
    • RLE.ParsedPattern

  • public class ParsedPattern
extends java.lang.Object
    Container for an RLE to ArrayListBoard parsing's output, containing the parsed pattern and the rule the pattern is designed for. Can be expanded to include metadata such as author, creation date etc.
